<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>
    * {
        margin: 0px;
        padding: 0px;
    }

    li {
        list-style: none;
    }

    div {
        width: 60%;
        margin-left: 20%;
        margin-right: 20%;
        border: 1px solid #169af3;
        margin-top: 30px;
    }

    div p {
        width: 100%;
        height: 50px;
        padding-top: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #169af3;
    }
    
    div li {
        width: 100%;
        height: 50px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    div li a{
        display: inline-block;
        width: 40%;
        height: 80%;
        margin-left: 30%;
        margin-right: 30%;
        background: #169af3;
        color: white;
        font-size: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #169af3;
        border-radius: 3px;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

</style>
<body>
    <div>
        <p>密码不正确</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/login">重新登录</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>